{"tid":1286874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」《一個慈父的自白》 ：回藍絲「一個強姦犯的自白」：","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T08:57:50.000Z","uid":215829,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"27c95ce9b0c43f7633c85d6b63e6b9da599159ab","tid":1286874,"uid":215829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"藍絲瘋傳！ 一個強姦犯的自白<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284046</a><br />\n ^<br />\n以上是藍絲瘋傳 形容抗爭者的訴求 <br />\n睇完先睇呢篇自白 <br />\n這篇文章是回應牠們的<br />\n<br />\n回應「一個強姦犯的自白」<br />\n<br />\n《一個慈父的自白》 作者以正苦第一人稱表述<br />\n<br />\n我一向也想與我的女兒發生性行為，她曾經被一對英國夫婦收養，並被西方的自由人權「洗腦」。在1-7-1997，她終於回歸了我的懷抱，我熱烈地歡迎她，可是她看似不太高興。於是我承諾在未來的五十年，她可享有自由和人權，只要不要分裂這個家庭。<br />\n<br />\n22年過去，我的性慾再按奈不住，於是我希望推出「女兒愛撫條例」，以替她按摩之名，令我可以和她有肌膚之親。可是，她不願接受，並稱我會以此為由把她強姦。我說她誤會了，可是她更反感，並帶了100萬人到我家抗議，要求我撒回條例，甚至去信那對英國夫婦和其他家庭，希望尋求支持。這丟光了我的面子。因為這是我的家事，與他們無關！！<br />\n<br />\n但是為未來的性行為我決定暫緩「女兒愛撫條例」遲點再非禮女兒<br />\n<br />\n可是她與示威者毫不領情，更動員200萬人表示不滿。於是我出動了我的警察朋友以武力解決他們，他們頭破血流。他們又不服氣，打碎了我數磈玻璃，非常暴力！！強烈譴責！！<br />\n<br />\n我灰心喪志，為何想愛撫女兒也受到阻撓，又不是強姦（至少not yet) <br />\n<br />\n我重申：女兒，我尊重你和朋友的自由，但必須和平理性非暴力；至於撒回「女兒愛撫條例」是不會發生，因為我不希望你任性，而強姦你是我作為父親的權利！<br />\n<br />\n你繼續抗爭也不會成功，因為我必須保持作為父親的管治威信，不能你說不強姦就不強姦。<br />\n<br />\n*同意請轉發 祝平安"},{"pid":"4f49dcea5d2f772fe45b7163e1a73c71e2298330","tid":1286874,"uid":215829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:54:18.000Z","msg":"請轉發給你的藍絲朋友 和建制派支持者"},{"pid":"5f66177759870bab148046808d2ba808fc0aaf61","tid":1286874,"uid":159327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"認同請轉發"},{"pid":"68524dd68a9048eacde3f199d49cf9df94d54266","tid":1286874,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742e5909bd2ef72403d8b4e9dc4630dec152892f","tid":1286874,"uid":62343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"秋月孝三都上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521d89427b09c4fe0c0f7ae5ac542380ecf34c7f","tid":1286874,"uid":44153,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"撒回<br />\n係6月見得最多嘅錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤呀"},{"pid":"f78a3fa9ff083efd33a45a9f3bfedacd5f372ebb","tid":1286874,"uid":215829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521d89427b09c4fe0c0f7ae5ac542380ecf34c7f","tid":1286874,"uid":44153,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"撒回<br />\n係6月見得最多嘅錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9643a4f0af613c4e51b74ee0f831fb8110cd9df","tid":1286874,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accc9a0251768ee842b79e9aef0352c64ac254f1","tid":1286874,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fb56665e25197e71d3c58ac2b6202d097fb6843","tid":1286874,"uid":215829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"推到藍絲見到"},{"pid":"1339122485ed5172cf5d3decfc2e8e2748a3fffe","tid":1286874,"uid":22707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好"},{"pid":"b8fa30f8181f47